title: Lunchbox Goes Undercover in Amy’s Neighborhood + Amy Gets Called Out By A Store Worker + Someone Loses the “Shell On” Challenge
itunes:title: Lunchbox Goes Undercover in Amy’s Neighborhood + Amy Gets Called Out By A Store Worker + Someone Loses the “Shell On” Challenge
description:
Amy says there’s been some shady activity going on in her neighborhood so Lunchbox goes to investigate. A store worker called Amy out after she tried to buy all of a certain product they had in stock. Someone loses the shell on challenge and has to eat something pretty gross!
